    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. The engine and transmission are fully operational, though you should expect the typical mechanical sounds and minor fluid seepage associated with a car of this age and mileage. The interior shows moderate wear, including some fading on the upholstery and minor scratches on the dashboard plastics. On the exterior, there are several noticeable paint chips and a few small dings, but no major structural damage. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to address cosmetic and minor mechanical upkeep over time.",
