    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exquisite example of automotive engineering, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle is offered in superlative condition, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in a state of absolute preservation. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most exacting clientele. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that remains aesthetically and functionally indistinguishable from its original showroom state. We welcome professional appraisal to confirm its peerless quality.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
