      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a meticulous history of climate-controlled storage and preventative maintenance. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail confirms its status as a collector-grade acquisition. This is a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of such caliber, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44850.0,
